				\begin{document}$$\mathcal {D}_U$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M62"><mml:msub><mml:mi mathvariant="script">D</mml:mi><mml:mi>U</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="10994_2017_5648_Article_IEq50.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. We will assume that we have <italic>N</italic> examples, out of which <inline-formula id="IEq51"><alternatives><tex-math id="M63">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
