				\begin{document}$$s=0$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M96"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>s</mml:mi><mml:mo>=</mml:mo><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="10994_2017_5648_Article_IEq67.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. In this way, the labelled set <inline-formula id="IEq68"><alternatives><tex-math id="M97">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
