				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$$\mathcal {D}_L$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M98"><mml:msub><mml:mi mathvariant="script">D</mml:mi><mml:mi>L</mml:mi></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="10994_2017_5648_Article_IEq68.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> comes from the joint distribution <inline-formula id="IEq69"><alternatives><tex-math id="M99">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
