</p><p>All three surrogates are valid&#x02014;in the following we determine whether they are also <italic>informed</italic>. To do this, we re-express the non-centrality parameters of the two valid surrogate tests, <inline-formula id="IEq126"><alternatives><tex-math id="M207">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
