</p></sec><sec id="FPar16"><title>Proof</title><p id="Par88">Sketches can be found in Appendix <xref rid="Sec41" ref-type="sec">B.5</xref>. <inline-formula id="IEq200"><alternatives><tex-math id="M359">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
