</p><sec id="Sec24"><title>Incorporating &#x0201c;exact&#x0201d; prior knowledge in sample size determination</title><p id="Par116">While the surrogate approach guarantees the same number of false positive errors, a direct consequence of Theorem <xref ref-type="sec" rid="FPar17">7</xref> is that using <inline-formula id="IEq306"><alternatives><tex-math id="M501">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
