				\begin{document}$$\kappa _{{\widetilde{Y}_0}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M504"><mml:msub><mml:mi mathvariant="italic">&#x003ba;</mml:mi><mml:msub><mml:mover accent="true"><mml:mi>Y</mml:mi><mml:mo stretchy="true">~</mml:mo></mml:mover><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:msub></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="10994_2017_5648_Article_IEq307.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> and &#x0201c;exact&#x0201d; prior knowledge over the <inline-formula id="IEq308"><alternatives><tex-math id="M505">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
