				\begin{document}$$H_0$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M682"><mml:msub><mml:mi>H</mml:mi><mml:mn>0</mml:mn></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="10994_2017_5648_Article_IEq398.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>) that <italic>X</italic> and <italic>Y</italic> are statistically independent given <inline-formula id="IEq399"><alternatives><tex-math id="M683">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
